{"tid":803681,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唉……今日開學點知比人串到喊 =.=","createTime":"2018-09-02T12:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T14:09:56.000Z","uid":123613,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e300b9da970445c59a8f5325531e9c4e22312dd","tid":803681,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"請各位高抬貴手，唔好屌我表情撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日見d同學成班圍埋一齊講野,我想搭下嗲,點知佢地話我講野1999=.= <br />\n我話:你班傻的嗎仔緊係聽唔明我講乜啦,我智商600,所以你地同我溝通唔到姐 <br />\n然後其中一個同學聽到之後話: 哦...原來我地智商差成400咁多,唔怪之得啦... <br />\n咁我又接住講: 算啦,我都唔介意既...點知佢地竟然話我弱智仔, <br />\n仲同我講:我地呢度每個人既智商都係1000以上,又叫我死開啦,白痴仔..咁＝︿＝ <br />\n聽到佢地咁講我忍唔住流左少少眼淚,然後跑走左,不過當時我仲係好型棍&gt;3&lt;, <br />\n我決定唔讀小一啦,以後日日上連登Hi 你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0241de46d7385e3f31165c5bd5bb17179a8336","tid":803681,"uid":197959,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"be2c4416b21a9fa5f0a75a95aaa4ca083d66a7fd","tid":803681,"uid":187076,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你up乜春？"},{"pid":"a23f9188a89e918caae937bd67d48cad29f81bb7","tid":803681,"uid":199211,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"